CustomField.description: This formula is created to calculate enquires this quarter last year. There is a corresponding number field that pulls the data out this formula and creates a roll up in Accounts corresponding field
CustomField.formula: IF(AND( Created_Date__c >= This_Qtr_Last_Year_Start_Date_Formula__c , Created_Date__c <= This_Qtr_Last_Year_End_Date_Formula__c ), 1, NULL)
CustomField.label: Enquiries This Quarter Last Year
